import FormControl from "@mui/material/FormControl";
import InputLabel from "@mui/material/InputLabel";
import Input from "@mui/material/Input";
import { ThemeProvider, createTheme } from "@mui/material/styles";
import { MuiThemeMod } from "../../css/muiTheme";
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';
import Paper from '@mui/material/Paper';
import Button from "@mui/material/Button";
import { useState, useEffect } from "react";

function ProjectForm() {
  const theme = createTheme(MuiThemeMod);
  const [project, setProject] = useState(projectData || {})
  function submitForm(){
    return console.log("vai se fuder")
  }

  function handleChange(e){
    setProject({
      ...project, [e.target.name]: e.target.value
    })
  }

  return (
    <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
    <Grid
      container
      spacing={3}
      justifyContent="center"
      alignItems="center"
      marginTop={2}
      >
      <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={10}>
        <Paper>
          <FormControl fullWidth>
          <InputLabel htmlFor="my-input" sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}>Project name:</InputLabel>
              <Input 
                id="email" 
                name="email" 
                type="text" 
                aria-describedby="my-helper-text"
              />
          </FormControl>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={10}>
        <Paper>
          <FormControl fullWidth>
          <InputLabel htmlFor="my-input" sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}>Email address:</InputLabel>
              <Input 
                id="email" 
                name="email" 
                type="text" 
                aria-describedby="my-helper-text" 
                placeholder="@.com" 
              />
          </FormControl>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={5}>
        <Paper>
          <FormControl fullWidth>
          <InputLabel htmlFor="my-input" sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}>Your phone:</InputLabel>
              <Input 
                id="phone" 
                name="phone" 
                type="text" 
                aria-describedby="my-helper-text" 
              />
          </FormControl>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={5}>
        <Paper>
          <FormControl fullWidth>
          <InputLabel htmlFor="my-input" sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}>Project budget:</InputLabel>
              <Input 
                id="budget" 
                name="budget" 
                type="number" 
                aria-describedby="my-helper-text" 
              />
          </FormControl>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={10}>
        <Paper>
          <FormControl fullWidth>
            <InputLabel htmlFor="my-input" sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}>Project description:</InputLabel>
              <Input 
                id="description" 
                name="description" type="description"
                aria-describedby="my-helper-text" 
              />
          </FormControl>
        </Paper>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={6} md={6} lg={5}>
        <Button variant="contained" color="primary" type="submit" fullWidth onClick={submitForm}         
        sx={{ color: theme.palette.secondary.main }}>
          Submit
        </Button>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  </ThemeProvider>
  );
}

export default ProjectForm;
